{
  "title": "Annotix: An Open-Source Desktop Platform for Machine Learning Dataset Annotation",
  "description": "<p>Annotix is an open-source cross-platform desktop application for ML dataset annotation, training and collaboration. It supports images, video, time series and tabular data, with built-in YOLO training, SAM-assisted annotation, 11 export formats and 8 import formats, and interfaces in 10 languages.</p>",
